@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequence Diagram (Team)

actor "Team Member" as User
participant "NextHire UI" as UI
participant "AI Backend" as AI
database "Database" as DB

User -> UI: Create Workspace & Assign Roles
UI -> DB: Save Team Data
DB --> UI: Success

UI -> AI: Request Project Recommendations
AI -> AI: Analyze Team Skills
AI --> UI: Return Recommendations
UI --> User: Display Projects

User -> UI: Upload Task / Commit Code
UI -> DB: Save Submission
UI -> AI: Trigger Task Verification
AI -> AI: Verify Code & Generate Insights
AI -> DB: Update Progress
AI --> UI: Return Verification Results
UI --> User: Display Results & Badges

AI -> DB: Fetch Weekly Data
AI -> AI: Generate Documentation & Reports
AI --> UI: Make Report Available
@enduml
